{"about_the_game":"On my 7th birthday, my grandma presented me with a hand-knitted cape. As I put it on and looked in the mirror, a spark was ignited within me I knew that I wanted to become a hero. And thus began my great adventure.I embarked on this journey full of hope and wonder, but I soon realized that life can be frustrating and the gap between my expectation and reality was vast. But there was one constant that I could always count on - the love of my family. It was like a cape that blew in the wind behind me, guiding me through the toughest times.<br><br>This experience has been the inspiration for this game, which is like chatting with a new friend. In the form of a game, we will together go back to our childhood, searching for precious memories. The game will feature different gameplay styles like lonely flying, fierce battle, nerve-wracking parkour, as well as various kinds of puzzles. It will be an emotional journey about love, dreams, courage and even silly memories, that I hope will inspire you as much as it did me<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Special narrative style<br></li><li>Different types of gameplay in one game<br></li><li>Unique hand-drawn style graphic and beautiful background music</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1489470/extras/escape_smaller\u526f\u672c.gif?t=1698324997\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1489470/extras/DreamFight.gif?t=1698324997\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1489470/extras/fly_smaller\u526f\u672c.gif?t=1698324997\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1489470/extras/gotoplay_smaller\u526f\u672c.gif?t=1698324997\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1489470/extras/TimdHero.smaller_c